#

Classic Beef Burrito with Salsa and Sour Cream

$12.99
720 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

BeefBurritoSalsaSour Cream

Description

A hearty classic beef burrito filled with seasoned ground beef, topped with fresh salsa and creamy sour cream, wrapped in a warm flour tortilla.

Ingredients

  • Ground Beef: 1 lb
  • Flour Tortillas: 4 large
  • Black Beans: 1 cup
  • Shredded Cheddar Cheese: 1 cup
  • Fresh Salsa: 1 cup
  • Sour Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Lettuce: 1 cup
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Taco Seasoning: 2 tbsp
